text: Kabakush () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kabakushsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 589 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Kabakush
